trans-unit.source: Enumerates the elements of an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Enumera os elementos de um <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: To get an IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A> method of an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter um IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract, use o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A>método de <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns the key and the value of the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref> entry.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a chave e o valor do atual <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"> </xref> entrada.

trans-unit.source: After an enumerator is created or after the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> method is called, the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before calling the GetEntry method; otherwise, the return value of GetEntry is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Após a criação de um enumerador ou depois do <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>método é chamado, o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>método deve ser chamado para avançar o enumerador para o primeiro elemento da coleção antes de chamar o método GetEntry; caso contrário, o valor de retorno de GetEntry é indefinido.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>

trans-unit.source: GetEntry also throws an exception if the last call to <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: GetEntry também gera uma exceção se a última chamada <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>retornado `false`, que indica o final da coleção.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: GetEntry does not move the position of the enumerator, and consecutive calls to GetEntry return the same object until either <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: GetEntry não move a posição do enumerador e chamadas consecutivas para GetEntry retornam o mesmo objeto até que o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>ou <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>é chamado.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"></xref> that contains the key and the value of the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref> entry.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"> </xref> que contém a chave e o valor atual <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"> </xref> entrada.
